social_posts.post_text: 7am Lindsey is never in the mood.
I just keep looking at photos of my dad wishing he was back. I can’t believe we lost him last night. I miss him already.

It’s been 10 days without my dad & I’ll miss him for a lifetime.

Fuck cancer.

Show casing some of my dads favorite things. 

Not giving a shit + Family + Cigars 

🖤
Forgot I never added from a few months ago 🧚🏻‍♀️
Needless to say… we couldn’t hang at the end.

“It’s easy to judge.
It’s more difficult to understand. 

Understanding requires compassion, patience, and willingness to believe that good hearts sometimes choose poor methods.

Through judging, we separate. 
Through understanding, we grow.”

I was given the opportunity to travel to learn & progress within the company which took me to SLC, Utah at our HQ location. 

It was such a good experience & was absolutely beautiful. 

My dad has been gone for 1.5 months & when he heard of this opportunity be presented to me he was excited for me. Unfortunately, he passed October 5th of last month. I just wish I could tell him all about it and show him the photos. 

Everything I do now is to make him proud & show I will be just fine.

You really wanted a big Christmas this year because you said it was going to be your last & the fact you didn’t make it to see it just really sucks. 

Mom is making sure your wants for this year are going to happen even though you’re not here for it.
